About A Boy	Contraception Deception	Andy thinks Laurie is pregnant, since she's showing all the usual signs. It turns out Andy never got the vasectomy Will badgered him not to get - then "faked" a vasectomy for Laurie's benefit.
About A Boy	Disappeared Dad	Marcus's father is a penguin researcher who would rather spend months isolated at Antarctic research bases than spend time with his son.
