Abbott Elementary	Sliding Scale of Idealism Versus Cynicism	On the idealism side, there's Janine and Jacob, who are still passionate about teaching and find various ways to work outside the system for their jobs. Barbara and Melissa are are on the cynicism side: they're both competent teachers, but far more jaded after spending years in the public school system dealing with low funding and apathetic faculty and parents.
