A Bit Of Fry And Laurie	Compensating for Something	One character whose genitals have been removed is offered a doberman, a combat jacket, a subscription to Guns and Ammo and a rusty white van, for the dual purpose of restoring his manhood and when the patient asks how he is supposed to urinate...Doctor (Laurie): Oh don't worry, that's the beauty of the system. When people see you wearing a combat jacket and driving round in a white van with Killer, the piss will be taken out of you constantly.
