A Different World	Where da White Women At?	Freddie's mother is white, and a handful of throwaway lines establish that Colonel Taylor's never-seen ex-wife is also. The Season 2 Valentine's Day episode has Maggie dancing with a black guy. Inverted with Kim and Freddie's cousin, Matthew.
