Akumaizer 3	Killed to Uphold the Masquerade	After Xavitan frees the humans the Akuma Clan kidnapped and brought to their lair in the first episode, the Akuma Clan goes on a killing spree of them in order to prevent the secrets of the Akuma Clan from spilling out.
