Ahsoka	Dramatic Irony	Senator Xiono dismisses the Imperial Remnant as a group of disorganized rogue warlords who don't pose a threat to the New Republic. This is exactly what Captain Pellaeon was hoping for, as the audience members who have already watched Season 3 of The Mandalorian will already know, as he stressed the need for the Remnant to keep a low profile to trick the New Republic into believing this so they could bide their time to regroup and replenish their ranks.
Ahsoka	Fantasy Counterpart Culture	Peridea seems to be In-Universe Feudal Japan. It's a closed off and isolated planet from the rest of civilization located in another galaxy, much like Japan used to be during the Edo Period. It has an alien native species dressed in red samurai-like armor and carrying Naginatas with them, and another one called the Noti which actually speaks Japanese. Thrawn even says that Peridea is where a Rōnin like Ahsoka belongs.
