AK Bingo	Idol Singer	Of course, all the girls are AKB48 members, and their sister groups and rival group Nogizaka46 are sometimes invited as well. However, there are some members in their late 20s and the members' behavior can often become very atypical of idols.
AK Bingo	I Just Want to Be Beautiful	
AK Bingo	I Just Want to Be You	In episode 533, Kubo Satone is revealed to have emulated Oguri Yui's fashion style and speech pattern, since they're both classic-type idols. Muramoto: Well, this is kinda scary. One of these days, Yuiyui will go missing and Sato-chan will be like "Yeah, Yuiyui's gone, what about it? By the way, have you seen Strolling Sato?"note A series where Satopii walks unplanned around town and do random things. (A picture of Satopii eating a turkey leg is shown) We should check whether Yuiyui still has her upper legs! "Yeah, this is Yuiyui leg..."
AK Bingo	I Just Want to Have Friends	Episode 401 sees Muramoto trying to improve his relationship with the members by challenging them to various matches, with cakes as reward for winning.
AK Bingo	Important Haircut	
