AK Bingo	Mistaken Nationality	In episode 522, the Taiwanese Ma Chia-Ling complains that Oguri Yui kept forgetting her homeland and mistaking it for Hong Kong, Shanghai, or Thailand. Muramoto, displaying blatant favoritism: If Yuiyui said that, it must be true, isn't it? ... Yuiyui, why did you forget it?Yuiyui: I didn't forget! I was just... mistaken.
