AK Bingo	Motor Mouth	
AK Bingo	Multiple Demographic Appeal	The show has invited guests and interviewed respondents from many different demographics.
AK Bingo	Never Trust a Title	Except for a very short opening segment in episode 238, they've never played Bingo on the show. They also don't say "Bingo!" as an interjection or catchphrase, as Muramoto is quickly informed when he does that in one of his early episodes. The title came from the group's sixth single "Bingo!", released in 2007. That song wasn't even the show's theme song, but it was used for the news segment jingle until 2016.
