Air City	Discreet Drink Disposal	In episode 5, Ye-won has finally badgered Ha-joon into a date. She is drinking heavily while Ha-joon isn't interested in drinking—he's pumping her for information about the mysterious top-secret patient in the airport hospital. So when she insists he take a shot, Ha-joon says "Look over there!", and throws his drink over his shoulder when her back is turned.
Air City	Dramatic Gun Cock	Sun-woo holding Ji-sung hostage at the beginning of episode 14 does this, presumably to be a little scarier.
