Air City	High Heel Hurt	Do-kyung is apparently bothered by her high heels as she's going to work, so she takes them off and starts walking across the airport concourse in her stocking feet. Ji-sung catches her, and it's a humanizing moment for the uptight Do-kyung.
Air City	How They Treat the Help	Ha-joon seems to know all the airport staff personally, chatting up the runway workers (and changing out a couple of runway lights himself when he notices one of the workers has a sprained ankle) and asking a lady who's collecting cardboard for recycling when her son is getting married. This becomes plot relevant in the second episode, when his familiarity with the staff causes him to realize that one of them's an impostor (the bad guy who escaped the hospital in the first episode).
