Alchemy Of Souls	The Four Gods	The Fire Bird is kept inside Jinyowon to prevent it from wrecking havoc on the world. The Black Tortoise also makes an appearance.
Alchemy Of Souls	Ghostly Chill	After using the Ice Stone's power to get rid of soul shifters, Jang Uk is regularly beset by wraiths who cause a general drop in temperature.
