Alchemy Of Souls	Morality Pet	Literally. Bu-yeon persuades Go Won to save and adopt a turtle by telling him that a good person like she sees he is will have mercy on it. The turtle comes to represent Won's better nature, and he claims that Jin Mu getting rid of it was the final straw that caused Won to turn against him.
