A League Of Their Own 2022	Hiding Your Heritage	The Mexican-American Lupe García is labelled the 'Spanish Striker' by the management and press, since saying she is of Spanish descent instead of Mexican is easier for the public to accept. Ironically, the actually-foreign Esti González doesn't need to hide her heritage, since at the time American society regarded Cubans as being of Spanish (European) descent and therefore classified as 'white' when it came to issues of segregation and law.
